title: Apple Gangnam will welcome first customers this Friday, March 31 in South Korea
description: SEOUL, South Korea, March 28, 2023--Apple® today previewed Apple Gangnam, located in Seoul’s bustling, world-famous Gangnam District. Apple Gangnam will offer an exciting space for customers to discover Apple’s incredible lineup of products and services, receive exceptional support from highly knowledgeable team members, and participate in free Today at Apple® sessions to learn how to get the most out of their products.

title: Apple Launches Apple Pay Later in the US
description: Apple Inc. has announced the delayed launch of its Apple Pay Later scheme.

title: Spadki na rynkach akcji w USA, koniec serii wzrostów S&P500 i DJIA
description: S&P500 stracił 0,2 proc., a Średnia Przemysłowa Dow Jones kończyła dzień 0,1 proc. zniżką. Największy spadek zanotował Nasdaq Composite, który stracił 0,45 proc.
